comments: Really interesting and engaging speaker. Knows alot about contemporary art. The class assignments were varied- from critiques to art making.
Refreshing view and interesting lectures. I would have liked more art making assignments cause I really enjoyed the ones we did!

I loved this class! Prof. Vose is kind and interested in modern art.There was a great slide selection, and she is knowledgable about art. She opened my eyes to a whole new world of art and when I was having trouble writing my paper, she met with me three times to go over it! The textbook was a bit hard.
